snippet.title: Why Do Narcissists' Have Babies?
snippet.description:
Narcissists are not capable of empathy, sympathy, compassion or even loving on a deep level.  Although they may show these emotions on a surface level, their brains are not wired to feel these emotions on a deep level. They may not even like children and have little patience or understanding them.

In this video I am going to go over the reasons why a narc will have babies/start a family, explain what is "mirroring" and go over AH's birth announcement.
